      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- Benchmark runner 可同时产出 JSON、Markdown、Prometheus textfile。\n- 这些面板展示的是最近几次离线评测结果，适合看基线回归趋势。\n- Search 重点看 Recall/NDCG/新鲜度满足率；Ingest 看 parse 成功率和结构质量；Summary 看 ROUGE/BERTScore；RAG 看 retrieval 与 citation。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 3,
          "max": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "notebooklm_benchmark_metric{benchmark=\"search\",metric_group=\"metrics\",metric_name=\"recall_at_k\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Recall@K",
